# Business Rules Document

This document outlines all use cases and permissions for each user type: **Admin**, **Teacher**, and **Student**.

> **Definition:**  
> **Manage** = **ADD, DELETE, UPDATE, VIEW**

---

# 1. Admin Rules

## 🧑‍💼 Users Database
- Admin can **ADD, DELETE, UPDATE, VIEW** users.
- Editable fields:
  - username  
  - email  
  - role  
  - password  
- Admin **cannot** edit:
  - nickname  
  - bias  
  - avatar  

## 🏫 Classes Database
- Admin can **manage** all classes.
- Admin can **manage student enrollment** (add/remove students).
- Admin can **assign or reassign teachers** to classes.
- Admin can **VIEW** class details.

## 🏫 Classroom Database
- Admin can **manage** all classrooms.
- Admin can **VIEW** classroom details.

## 📝 Assignments Database
- Admin can **VIEW** all assignments.

## 📤 Submission Database
- Admin can **VIEW** all submissions.

## 📅 Attendance Database
- Admin can **VIEW** all attendance records.

## 📚 Content Database
- Admin can **VIEW** all content.

---

# 2. Teacher Rules

## 🧑‍🏫 Users Database
- Teacher can **UPDATE** their own profile fields:
  - nickname  
  - bias  
  - avatar  
- Teacher cannot edit:
  - username  
  - email  
  - role  
  - password 

## 🏫 Classes Database
- Teacher can **VIEW** only their assigned classes.
- Teacher can **manage attendance** for their classes (ADD, UPDATE, VIEW).

## 🏫 Classroom Database
- Teacher can **UPDATE** and **VIEW** their classroom linked to their classes.
- Teacher cannot add or delete classrooms.

## 📝 Assignments Database
- Teacher can **manage** assignments for their classes.
- Teacher can **request additional submissions** from students.
- Teacher can **VIEW** all their class assignments.

## 📤 Submission Database
- Teacher can **VIEW** submissions from their students.
- Teacher can **MARK / GRADE** submissions.
- Teacher cannot delete or update submissions (except grading).

## 📚 Content Database
- Teacher can **manage** content for their classes (ADD, DELETE, UPDATE, VIEW).

---

# 3. Student Rules

## 👤 Users Database
- Student can **UPDATE** their own profile fields:
  - nickname  
  - bias  
  - avatar  
- Student cannot edit:
  - username  
  - email  
  - role  
  - password  

## 🏫 Classes Database
- Student can **VIEW** their own class information only.

## 🏫 Classroom Database
- Student can **VIEW** their classroom information only.

## 📝 Assignments Database
- Student can **VIEW** their assignments.

## 📤 Submission Database
- Student can **ADD** their own submissions.
- Student can **VIEW** their own submissions.
- Student cannot update or delete submissions after submission (unless resubmission is allowed).

## 📅 Attendance Database
- Student can **VIEW** their attendance.
- Student can **DISPUTE** attendance records.

## 📚 Content Database
- Student can **VIEW** content for their classes.

